Docs.summary: Specifies the Ids of special runtime types.
Docs.remarks: Only types explicitly mentioned in "Co-located core types" spec (https://github.com/dotnet/roslyn/blob/master/docs/compilers/Co-located%20core%20types.md) can be in this enum. The following things should be in sync: 1) SpecialType enum 2) names in SpecialTypes.EmittedNames array.
